{
  "name": "RPlog_Tattling_in_the_Temple",
  "title": "Tattling in the Temple",
  "summary": "In the sunlit solarium of the Jedi temple on New Alderaan, Ord Mantell, Ambassador Ambrosia Delgard seeks a private audience with Master Luke Skywalker to deliver troubling news. Reluctant in her role as messenger, she relays a warning passed to her by the opportunist Zeak Oppenhiemer: Johanna Te Da'nan intends to offer herself as apprentice to the Sith Lord Vidious in a reckless scheme to usurp power from Vadim and perhaps slay Vidious herself. Luke receives the report calmly, acknowledging that the desperate plan rings true to Johanna's loyal but reckless character, and gently presses Ambrosia for details while sensing the recent trauma weighing on her. The conversation turns to her young daughter Gabi, whose nightly terrors haunt them both, before the scene pauses and dissolves into a round of irreverent out-of-character banter between the two players.",
